idle hands is a 1999 american stoner black comedy body horror film directed by rodman flender , written by terri hughes and ron &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , and starring devon sawa , seth green , elden henson , jessica alba , and vivica a. fox . the main plot follows the life of an average lazy stoner teenager , anton tobias ( sawa ) , whose hand becomes possessed and goes on a killing spree , even after being cut off from his arm . the film 's title is based on the saying " idle hands are the devil 's &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; " or " idle hands do the devil 's work " . the film was a critical and commercial failure , grossing a little over $ 4 million from an estimated $ 25 million budget .